# Monorepo Plugin Structure

## Directory Layout

```
medusa-plugins/
├── packages/
│   ├── payment-{name}/              # @peyya/medusa-payment-{name}
│   │   └── src/providers/{name}/
│   ├── fulfillment-{name}/          # @peyya/medusa-fulfillment-{name}
│   │   └── src/providers/{name}/
│   ├── auth-{name}/                 # @peyya/medusa-auth-{name}
│   │   └── src/providers/{name}/
│   ├── plugin-{name}/               # @peyya/medusa-plugin-{name}
│   │   └── src/modules/{name}/
│   └── sdk/                         # @peyya/medusa-plugins (umbrella)
├── docs/
│   ├── ARCHITECTURE.md
│   ├── plugins/                     # Category-level design docs
│   └── providers/                   # Provider-specific implementation docs
├── turbo.json
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml
└── package.json
```

## Naming Conventions

| Type | Package Name | Directory |
|------|-------------|-----------|
| Payment provider | `@peyya/medusa-payment-{name}` | `packages/payment-{name}/` |
| Fulfillment provider | `@peyya/medusa-fulfillment-{name}` | `packages/fulfillment-{name}/` |
| Auth provider | `@peyya/medusa-auth-{name}` | `packages/auth-{name}/` |
| Feature plugin | `@peyya/medusa-plugin-{name}` | `packages/plugin-{name}/` |
| Umbrella SDK | `@peyya/medusa-plugins` | `packages/sdk/` |

Module names MUST be camelCase (never dashes): `"recommendations"`, `"searchIntelligence"`, `"agenticCommerce"`

## Architecture Mapping

| Category | Base Class | Export | Plugin Path |
|----------|-----------|--------|-------------|
| Payments | `AbstractPaymentProvider` | `ModuleProvider(Modules.PAYMENT, ...)` | `src/providers/` |
| Fulfillment | `AbstractFulfillmentProvider` | `ModuleProvider(Modules.FULFILLMENT, ...)` | `src/providers/` |
| Auth | `AbstractAuthModuleProvider` | `ModuleProvider(Modules.AUTH, ...)` | `src/providers/` |
| Intelligence | `MedusaService` | `Module(...)` | `src/modules/` |
| Agentic Commerce | `MedusaService` | `Module(...)` | `src/modules/` + `src/api/` |

## Dependency Rules

- `@medusajs/framework` → `devDependencies` + `peerDependencies` (same version range)
- Third-party SDKs (stripe, klarna, postnord-api) → `dependencies`
- `@swc/core` → `devDependencies` (required by Medusa plugin CLI)
- Shared workspace packages → `"workspace:*"` protocol
- Never pin exact Medusa versions across packages

## NPM Keywords (required for all packages)

- `medusa-v2` + `medusa-plugin-integration`
- Category: `medusa-plugin-payment`, `medusa-plugin-shipping`, `medusa-plugin-auth`, or `medusa-plugin-other`

## Build & Publish

- Each package builds with `npx medusa plugin:build`
- Changesets for independent versioning per package
- Turborepo caches builds and runs only changed packages
- Never publish packages that don't pass `tsc --noEmit`

## Linear Integration

- Initiative: "Medusa JS Plugins"
- Projects: one per category (Monorepo Infrastructure, Payments, Fulfillment, Auth, Intelligence, Agentic Commerce)
- Milestones: one per provider/plugin within each project
- Consult `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` for the master plan
